flowchart LR
    Internet[Internet] --> Router[Edge Router]
    Router --> DMZ[Public Ingress Path]
    Router --> LAN[Private LAN]
    DMZ --> Nginx[NGINX]
    Admin[Cloudflared or SSH Access] --> Bastion[SSH Bastion]
    LAN --> DockerHost[Docker Host]
    Bastion --> DockerHost
    Nginx --> PublicApps[Public Web Apps]
    Nginx --> SelectedPrivate[Selective Private App Exposure]
    DockerHost --> ComposeProjects[Multiple Compose Projects]
    ComposeProjects --> DataDirs[Per-Service Root and Data Paths]
    DataDirs --> Backups[backups/docker-compose timestamp sets]
